E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('994','79','县旅游局','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhaoshangyinzi/zhaoshangdongtai/2011-11-28/521b444b069bd6f49479937d050b4137.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">图为海航集团华南控股有限公司董事长何家福向市长任振鹤赠送机模<br />\r\n</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhaoshangyinzi/zhaoshangdongtai/2011-11-28/a0294d6deb78927a2a697c08a1912193.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">图为经贸洽谈会签约仪式现场<br />\r\n</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">鄂港粤经贸洽谈会圆满落幕。签约仪式上，县委书记熊征宇与广东长鹿投资有限公司董事长邹颂炫正式签订投资合同，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的湖北长鹿农庄项目落户嘉鱼。湖北省省长王国生、广东省代省长朱小丹出席会议并见证签约。咸宁市市长任振鹤参加经贸洽谈活动，并实地考察长鹿农庄和海航集团华南控股有限公司。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">湖北长鹿农庄项目一期投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，将在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年内完成建设并投入运营。该项目位于嘉鱼县陆溪镇，南临陆水河，西临长江，西南距三国赤壁古战场仅</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">公里，总规划面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里，区域内拥有渗子湖、珍湖和虎山林场，自然风光优美，生态保护良好。项目区规划有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个主题游乐园和近</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个风格各异的主题酒店、度假酒店、会所，主要面向大众市场和新生代年轻群体，设计年接待能力</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万人次。项目建成后，将会与&ldquo;嘉鱼海航世界&rdquo;互为呼应和补充，形成以陆口生态文化旅游圈、泛三湖连江旅游经济圈为两轮驱动，以度假、游乐、休闲为主题的综合旅游区。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">任振鹤在会见广东长鹿投资有限公司和海航集团华南控股有限公司主要负责人时表示，真诚欢迎两家有实力的投资商落户咸宁，并将全力为项目开发建设做好服务，鼓励两家企业在更宽广的领域与咸宁开展更深入的合作，推进咸宁作为鄂南经济强市和生态旅游新城的建设。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据熊征宇介绍，今后的一段时期，县委、县政府继续将旅游业作为推动超常规发展的重点产业，瞄准建设&ldquo;旅游强县&rdquo;目标，打造华中优秀旅游目的地，加快旅游项目建设，打响&ldquo;诗经嘉鱼，二乔故里&rdquo;的旅游品牌。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");

